data.description: This well-equipped distinctive four-bedroom (2 main-1 guest with own entrance -1 guest used as office), 3 bathroom home features an impressive stone backdrop to the great room pellet stove that adds rustic charm. The custom tile and unique architectural elements throughout make it both fascinating and practical. Additionally, it's a horse property with a powder-coated steel fenced arena, and a barn (horse grooming/stalls) with running water and electricity. There is an attached extended 2 car garage with abundant storage and a detached facility used as either a 2 car garage/workshop or as a horse facility/barn or both. This property with breathtaking mountain views is truly one of a kind and is suitable for anyone looking for a functional living space and a serene and scenic retreat.
